message: The 'growth serum' is your primary tool. It adds a 'grown' feature and value to items based on their original size (Small: 5, Medium: 10, Large: 15). To maximize your score, use the 'growth serum' on the two largest available ingredients, then combine those two 'grown' items. message: Use 'growth serum' on all items; it adds 'grown' feature and value (small=5, medium=10, large=15). Never use 'mutation catalyst', it always makes items negative.
